1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 34 =

20
00:01:39,660 --> 00:01:40,860
Stop following me!

21
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:42,820
Or you’ll all be beheaded!

22
00:02:08,940 --> 00:02:11,820
I’m sorry. It’s broken.

23
00:02:15,540 --> 00:02:16,620
I just started learning to make it.

24
00:02:17,340 --> 00:02:18,340
It looked bad.

25
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:21,220
I’ll make you a better one.

26
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:30,220
I...I simply wanted

27
00:02:30,220 --> 00:02:32,660
to give my favorite thing to Yaoyao,

28
00:02:34,180 --> 00:02:36,500
but father didn’t let me explain.

29
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:41,220
Do you have to?

30
00:02:43,180 --> 00:02:44,740
Doesn’t His Majesty trust you enough?

31
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:47,820
But...

32
00:02:51,580 --> 00:02:52,700
His Majesty is kindhearted.

33
00:02:53,780 --> 00:02:54,900
He pities Madam Zhang.

34
00:02:58,540 --> 00:02:59,700
Pity her?

35
00:03:02,060 --> 00:03:04,220
She grew up without a father.

36
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:07,380
Then she lost her own child.

37
00:03:08,780 --> 00:03:09,860
All she can depend on

38
00:03:10,340 --> 00:03:11,980
is His Majesty.

39
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:28,060
Zuixinglai was coughing and having a fever

40
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:31,300
so I didn’t attend the Double Ninth Banquet.

41
00:03:31,380 --> 00:03:32,660
How could this happen?

42
00:03:34,060 --> 00:03:35,860
I’m not taking my daughter’s side,

43
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:38,820
but Huirou always likes her brothers and sisters.

44
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:42,580
That woman is mean and narrow-minded,

45
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:43,940
so she thinks the worst

46
00:03:43,940 --> 00:03:45,020
of everyone.

47
00:03:45,340 --> 00:03:46,300
His Majesty has arrived.

48
00:03:51,220 --> 00:03:51,860
Your Majesty.

49
00:03:52,380 --> 00:03:53,140
Your Majesty.

50
00:03:53,780 --> 00:03:54,940
Is Zuixinglai getting better?

51
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:58,180
Although his fever is gone,

52
00:03:59,260 --> 00:04:00,260
he still coughs.

53
00:04:02,540 --> 00:04:04,660
Ask Physician Lin to check him tomorrow

54
00:04:04,780 --> 00:04:06,020
and prescribe herbs

55
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:07,300
if necessary.

56
00:04:07,780 --> 00:04:09,260
If the Imperial Pharmacy doesn’t have them,

57
00:04:09,860 --> 00:04:11,140
ask people to check the Treasury

58
00:04:11,460 --> 00:04:13,540
or buy some from the outside.

59
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:15,540
Thank you, Your Majesty.

60
00:04:23,460 --> 00:04:25,060
Is it still too early

61
00:04:25,580 --> 00:04:27,780
to teach him

62
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:29,500
to read and write?

63
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:31,140
That can wait.

64
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:38,020
Fine. I’ll listen to you.

65
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:42,220
Over the years,

66
00:04:42,940 --> 00:04:44,140
under the Empress’s guidance,

67
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:45,500
you’ve also become more mannered.

68
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:49,260
I’m a member of the harem,

69
00:04:49,820 --> 00:04:51,700
so I ought to follow the rules

70
00:04:52,260 --> 00:04:54,140
and Her Highness’s guidance.

71
00:04:59,820 --> 00:05:00,580
Where’s Huirou?

72
00:05:01,340 --> 00:05:02,260
Is she in her room?

73
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:05,340
She’s gone to bed.

74
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:09,180
I’ll go check on her.

75
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:19,460
Your Majesty.

76
00:05:51,340 --> 00:05:52,140
Huirou.

77
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:54,620
Look what I have for you.

78
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:02,220
These desserts and plums

79
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:03,580
are freshly made.

80
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:05,100
The new chefs

81
00:06:05,180 --> 00:06:06,980
can bake pastries of the south.

82
00:06:06,980 --> 00:06:08,460
Even I haven’t had them before.

83
00:06:08,940 --> 00:06:10,060
These are made

84
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:11,900
for today’s banquet.

85
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:14,220
I packed one for each kind

86
00:06:14,220 --> 00:06:15,500
that tastes the best for you.

87
00:06:17,380 --> 00:06:18,380
It won’t taste as good

88
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:19,580
tomorrow.

89
00:06:28,340 --> 00:06:29,660
What a heavy sleeper!

90
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:37,420
Come.

91
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:43,420
Take this.

92
00:06:44,380 --> 00:06:45,180
Eat them yourself

93
00:06:45,700 --> 00:06:46,460
or

94
00:06:46,460 --> 00:06:48,140
share them with other maids.

95
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:50,140
Alright. Off you go.

96
00:06:58,740 --> 00:06:59,980
Since princess is asleep,

97
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:01,660
let’s go back.

98
00:07:20,580 --> 00:07:21,740
Has my father left?

99
00:07:36,580 --> 00:07:37,660
Still hiding yourself?

100
00:07:41,980 --> 00:07:43,860
Hold it. Do not laugh,

101
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:45,980
or everyone will know you’re gap-toothed.

102
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:50,620
That was you when you were little.

103
00:07:53,540 --> 00:07:54,660
You aren’t mad at me anymore?

104
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:01,780
I’m still a bit upset.

105
00:08:06,780 --> 00:08:08,180
You did nothing wrong earlier.

106
00:08:09,340 --> 00:08:10,820
I did raise my voice

107
00:08:10,820 --> 00:08:11,660
to you,

108
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:13,580
but I never meant to scold you.

109
00:08:15,420 --> 00:08:16,540
I know

110
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:18,500
you love your younger sister

111
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:19,540
and meant to give her

112
00:08:19,660 --> 00:08:21,460
your treasure

113
00:08:22,020 --> 00:08:23,580
but were wronged by Madam Zhang

114
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:26,940
and yelled at by me.

115
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:33,100
Your third sister was weak

116
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:34,140
when she arrived

117
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:37,500
and her condition

118
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:38,540
worsened with time.

119
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:41,860
Neither Madam Zhang or I

120
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:44,380
could do anything about it.

121
00:08:46,140 --> 00:08:47,100
She had to look after her sick daughter

122
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:48,460
all the time

123
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:52,220
when she was only 16

124
00:08:52,660 --> 00:08:54,340
and practically a child herself.

125
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:56,980
It was cruel to her.

126
00:08:58,140 --> 00:08:59,660
When people were sad,

127
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:02,300
venting anger on others
might make them feel better.

128
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:06,620
That doll was made to curse others,

129
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:07,780
so she targeted at you.

130
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:10,340
She’s too stubborn

131
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:12,780
to be reasoned with.

132
00:09:13,660 --> 00:09:14,500
Right now,

133
00:09:15,540 --> 00:09:18,140
your fourth sister is her life.

134
00:09:18,380 --> 00:09:19,460
Since the tragic death

135
00:09:19,460 --> 00:09:20,620
of her first daughter,

136
00:09:21,380 --> 00:09:22,340
she’s become more scared

137
00:09:22,780 --> 00:09:24,140
and paranoid.

138
00:09:24,460 --> 00:09:25,540
Her fear

139
00:09:26,380 --> 00:09:28,340
clouds her judgment.

140
00:09:30,180 --> 00:09:31,340
I know

141
00:09:31,940 --> 00:09:33,100
I hurt your feelings today,

142
00:09:33,300 --> 00:09:34,500
but I could only separate you two

143
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:35,660
at the moment.

144
00:09:36,980 --> 00:09:38,580
I know you’re rational

145
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:39,420
and considerate.

146
00:09:40,860 --> 00:09:41,900
Madam Zhang

147
00:09:44,620 --> 00:09:46,380
lost her mind

148
00:09:47,540 --> 00:09:48,900
and couldn’t listen to anything.

149
00:09:55,140 --> 00:09:55,940
Father,

150
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:59,340
my fourth sister will be fine.

151
00:10:02,620 --> 00:10:03,340
Father,

152
00:10:05,060 --> 00:10:07,220
you said Madam Zhang was sad,

153
00:10:08,540 --> 00:10:10,580
so she had to vent her anger on others,

154
00:10:11,700 --> 00:10:14,700
yet you kept your sadness all to yourself.

155
00:10:17,780 --> 00:10:20,140
Father, I promise

156
00:10:20,780 --> 00:10:22,660
I won’t offend Madam Zhang again.

157
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:26,300
However mean she is to me,

158
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:27,500
I’ll tolerate her.

159
00:10:28,780 --> 00:10:30,540
If I’m too mad...

160
00:10:34,180 --> 00:10:34,940
Father,

161
00:10:35,420 --> 00:10:37,580
you’re criticized by officials all the time.

162
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:39,660
Her Highness says

163
00:10:39,980 --> 00:10:41,460
they aren’t always right

164
00:10:42,980 --> 00:10:44,780
and they blame you for everything.

165
00:10:45,820 --> 00:10:47,300
When there was a disaster,

166
00:10:47,780 --> 00:10:48,980
they’d wonder

167
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:51,300
if you indulged yourself with pleasure,

168
00:10:53,540 --> 00:10:55,860
or if you spent too much time in the harem.

169
00:10:56,540 --> 00:10:58,340
How did you manage

170
00:10:59,060 --> 00:11:00,580
to stay unaffected?

171
00:11:09,060 --> 00:11:10,300
What happened this time?

172
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:13,140
Why the long face?

173
00:11:14,660 --> 00:11:16,060
Didn’t Madam Zhang

174
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:18,580
have a big win today?

175
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:21,460
She beat

176
00:11:21,940 --> 00:11:23,860
His Majesty’s most beloved daughter,

177
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:25,940
Princess Fukang, in public.

178
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:29,300
You knew very well

179
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:32,460
without that cursing doll,

180
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:34,300
she wouldn’t have targeted

181
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:35,660
at Princess Fukang.

182
00:11:37,740 --> 00:11:39,300
You knew everything

183
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:40,340
about that doll.

184
00:11:41,020 --> 00:11:42,500
Yang Huaimin and Xia Song

185
00:11:42,540 --> 00:11:43,900
didn’t tell you to do that.

186
00:11:43,900 --> 00:11:45,180
It was for your personal grudge.

187
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:46,980
You’re close to Yang Huaimin,

188
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:47,940
but it doesn’t mean I can’t touch you.

189
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:54,780
Are you here to search my place?

190
00:11:58,140 --> 00:12:00,500
Fine. I’ll tell you the truth.

191
00:12:01,620 --> 00:12:03,180
I did make that doll.

192
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:05,220
It was to vent my anger.

193
00:12:06,460 --> 00:12:07,700
Chuyue was weak

194
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:08,660
since she was born.

195
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:10,020
She’d never grow up.

196
00:12:10,860 --> 00:12:12,460
You really think she died of my curse?

197
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:14,580
What about Yaoyao?

198
00:12:16,660 --> 00:12:17,580
That handkerchief...

199
00:12:17,660 --> 00:12:18,780
That handkerchief

200
00:12:18,780 --> 00:12:19,740
wasn’t the only thing.

201
00:12:23,380 --> 00:12:24,180
Lantiao...

202
00:12:27,980 --> 00:12:29,540
Believe it or not,

203
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:33,340
those paper mulberry flowers weren’t for Yaoyao.

204
00:12:35,260 --> 00:12:36,900
I remember it vividly

205
00:12:37,980 --> 00:12:39,340
that back then when we were at the Institute,

206
00:12:40,020 --> 00:12:41,180
there were paper mulberries.

207
00:12:43,180 --> 00:12:44,580
During the blooming season,

208
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:47,020
she’d have runny eyes and nose.

209
00:12:48,380 --> 00:12:49,780
Her nose would become red

210
00:12:51,140 --> 00:12:52,220
and her lips would swell.

211
00:12:53,460 --> 00:12:54,460
She looked hideous.

212
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:01,820
Why?

213
00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:06,300
Why were you so partial to her?

214
00:13:06,980 --> 00:13:09,020
I was the most obedient one to you.

215
00:13:10,380 --> 00:13:11,780
Many people believed

216
00:13:11,780 --> 00:13:12,740
I was more attractive

217
00:13:12,740 --> 00:13:13,780
and tenderer than her,

218
00:13:15,740 --> 00:13:16,700
but you only favored her

219
00:13:16,780 --> 00:13:18,620
and hooked her up with His Majesty

220
00:13:18,620 --> 00:13:19,740
to enjoy fame and wealth,

221
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:22,980
leaving me nothing at all.

222
00:13:29,220 --> 00:13:30,620
Pick a mansion

223
00:13:31,740 --> 00:13:32,580
in the west suburb.

224
00:13:34,420 --> 00:13:35,340
What for?

225
00:13:39,740 --> 00:13:41,020
Take it as my compensation

226
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:42,380
for your loss.

227
00:13:44,620 --> 00:13:46,100
I can give you unlimited money,

228
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:48,180
a mansion

229
00:13:48,780 --> 00:13:50,980
and other valuables.

230
00:13:53,460 --> 00:13:55,140
Once you get out, you can enjoy your life.

231
00:13:56,700 --> 00:13:58,740
You don’t need to do this anymore

232
00:13:59,580 --> 00:14:01,140
or pander to Yang Huaimin.

233
00:14:07,780 --> 00:14:09,460
You want me to leave

234
00:14:11,340 --> 00:14:13,140
and offer me money and a big house?

235
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:16,340
I see.

236
00:14:17,260 --> 00:14:17,980
Right now,

237
00:14:17,980 --> 00:14:19,460
I’m a nobody in her eyes,

238
00:14:20,780 --> 00:14:22,420
not the one she was eager

239
00:14:22,420 --> 00:14:23,700
to skin alive.

240
00:14:26,860 --> 00:14:29,380
When she stayed with His Majesty,

241
00:14:30,740 --> 00:14:32,180
you know what my life was like

242
00:14:32,180 --> 00:14:33,420
at the Institute?

243
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:40,180
Wasn’t it you

244
00:14:40,860 --> 00:14:42,620
who set her up at that time?

245
00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:45,140
Didn’t she

246
00:14:45,140 --> 00:14:46,260
pick on me at first?

247
00:14:49,100 --> 00:14:49,780
Alright.

248
00:14:52,780 --> 00:14:55,180
The past is the past.

249
00:14:55,780 --> 00:14:56,740
If you leave now,

250
00:14:57,380 --> 00:14:58,900
you can enjoy

251
00:14:58,900 --> 00:14:59,660
a well-off life.

252
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:00,620
I won’t leave!

253
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:03,060
I promise

254
00:15:04,180 --> 00:15:05,500
I won’t touch her again.

255
00:15:07,540 --> 00:15:08,700
She already lost one daughter.

256
00:15:10,140 --> 00:15:11,500
And I almost killed Yaoyao

257
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:12,460
by accident.

258
00:15:13,660 --> 00:15:15,020
She and I are even.

259
00:15:18,860 --> 00:15:19,820
From now on,

260
00:15:20,660 --> 00:15:22,580
we’re on the same boat.

261
00:15:23,940 --> 00:15:25,020
If she sinks,

262
00:15:25,460 --> 00:15:26,420
we’ll be drowned, too.

263
00:15:27,580 --> 00:15:28,740
What do you want?

264
00:15:29,100 --> 00:15:30,100
I’m not going anywhere.

265
00:15:42,660 --> 00:15:43,900
This is Shi Jie’s letter to Fu Bi

266
00:15:44,860 --> 00:15:46,220
that your lover Chief Xia is eager to get.

267
00:15:47,180 --> 00:15:48,340
I beat him to it.

268
00:16:14,620 --> 00:16:15,460
Are there any taboo words?

269
00:16:16,180 --> 00:16:17,300
Or are they involved

270
00:16:17,980 --> 00:16:19,500
in bribery and corruption, too?

271
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:22,500
That I don’t know.

272
00:16:24,180 --> 00:16:24,940
Anyway,

273
00:16:24,940 --> 00:16:26,580
this is the letter that Chief Xia wants.

274
00:16:34,020 --> 00:16:34,820
How did you get it?

275
00:16:35,380 --> 00:16:36,380
All my attempts failed.

276
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:39,580
Tao at Fu Bi’s mansion

277
00:16:40,180 --> 00:16:41,740
wouldn’t work for you.

278
00:16:42,900 --> 00:16:43,860
Back at the Institute,

279
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:46,140
Zhang Bihan tortured her,

280
00:16:46,300 --> 00:16:47,820
but you turned a blind eye to it.

281
00:16:49,420 --> 00:16:50,700
When she made a name in the palace,

282
00:16:51,020 --> 00:16:53,580
Tao was scared and weaker than me,

283
00:16:54,540 --> 00:16:55,500
so she left the palace.

284
00:16:56,340 --> 00:16:57,620
She had a hard time at first

285
00:16:58,140 --> 00:16:59,340
and had to live on my handout.

286
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:01,060
What do you think now?

287
00:17:02,780 --> 00:17:05,700
I can help you for sure.

288
00:17:07,300 --> 00:17:09,020
Don’t forget my credit.

289
00:17:10,540 --> 00:17:11,820
How could I

290
00:17:11,820 --> 00:17:14,420
not be affected by their endless criticism?

291
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:16,820
When they stepped on my nerves,

292
00:17:16,820 --> 00:17:18,540
I said to myself

293
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:20,180
that even if their criticism

294
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:21,460
was wrong,

295
00:17:21,580 --> 00:17:22,740
it showed their loyalty.

296
00:17:23,700 --> 00:17:25,060
Even if they wronged me,

297
00:17:25,820 --> 00:17:27,940
that was because they couldn’t

298
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:29,100
be with me all the time

299
00:17:29,180 --> 00:17:30,580
to know the whole truth.

300
00:17:31,460 --> 00:17:32,620
Like that,

301
00:17:33,420 --> 00:17:36,180
I could calm myself down most of the time.

302
00:17:37,980 --> 00:17:39,380
What if you failed

303
00:17:39,940 --> 00:17:41,620
and you were still mad?

304
00:17:44,580 --> 00:17:46,700
Then I’d...

305
00:17:49,580 --> 00:17:51,100
take a deep breath

306
00:17:51,980 --> 00:17:53,100
and swallow the bad words

307
00:17:53,860 --> 00:17:57,020
at the tip of my tongue.

308
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:02,940
Next,

309
00:18:03,660 --> 00:18:04,420
I’d say

310
00:18:04,420 --> 00:18:06,260
different things to myself

311
00:18:06,460 --> 00:18:07,460
according to

312
00:18:07,460 --> 00:18:09,020
who I was dealing with.

313
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:11,580
What...

314
00:18:11,860 --> 00:18:12,980
What do you mean?

315
00:18:13,980 --> 00:18:16,060
For example, if Fan Zhongyan

316
00:18:16,260 --> 00:18:17,980
was giving me a lecture,

317
00:18:18,980 --> 00:18:20,420
I’d tell myself

318
00:18:21,300 --> 00:18:22,980
that he lost his father when he was little.

319
00:18:23,020 --> 00:18:24,100
When he was old enough to study,

320
00:18:24,260 --> 00:18:26,220
he had to live in a temple.

321
00:18:27,660 --> 00:18:28,540
It was cold in winter

322
00:18:28,540 --> 00:18:29,740
and had mosquitoes in summer.

323
00:18:30,460 --> 00:18:32,060
He only had a handful of millet to eat every day.

324
00:18:32,380 --> 00:18:33,460
A pot of millet congee

325
00:18:33,460 --> 00:18:34,940
was his two meals per day.

326
00:18:35,660 --> 00:18:37,060
And he had to go to bed early,

327
00:18:37,060 --> 00:18:38,380
or he’d be too starving

328
00:18:38,380 --> 00:18:39,740
to sleep through the rest of the night.

329
00:18:40,540 --> 00:18:41,300
I thought to myself

330
00:18:42,420 --> 00:18:43,540
that I had 20 more years

331
00:18:43,540 --> 00:18:45,580
of mutton and candied plums than him after all.

332
00:18:46,340 --> 00:18:49,220
Just let him speak.

333
00:18:51,980 --> 00:18:53,500
If it was Yu Jing...

334
00:18:55,660 --> 00:18:57,620
That man could talk my ears off.

335
00:18:58,060 --> 00:18:59,140
I told him repeatedly

336
00:18:59,660 --> 00:19:01,140
that he was right;

337
00:19:01,140 --> 00:19:02,420
I’d consider his advice

338
00:19:02,420 --> 00:19:03,420
and reconvene another day,

339
00:19:04,260 --> 00:19:06,500
but he still wouldn’t stop.

340
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:08,700
Another thing is,

341
00:19:08,700 --> 00:19:09,660
he has poor hygiene

342
00:19:09,860 --> 00:19:10,620
and seldom takes a bath.

343
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:13,260
When he stood close to me,

344
00:19:13,340 --> 00:19:14,940
that stink could suffocate me.

345
00:19:17,340 --> 00:19:18,260
Then...

346
00:19:18,740 --> 00:19:21,020
you couldn’t even take a deep breath.

347
00:19:21,380 --> 00:19:22,620
What would you do?

348
00:19:23,740 --> 00:19:24,780
I thought...

349
00:19:28,060 --> 00:19:28,940
This is our secret.

350
00:19:28,940 --> 00:19:30,220
Keep it between us.

351
00:19:32,540 --> 00:19:33,740
I won’t tell others.

352
00:19:38,020 --> 00:19:39,060
I thought

353
00:19:39,660 --> 00:19:41,820
he really stank.

354
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:42,980
Even his daughter

355
00:19:43,140 --> 00:19:44,300
didn’t want his hug.

356
00:19:44,900 --> 00:19:45,780
She’d run away immediately

357
00:19:46,340 --> 00:19:47,900
and would rather study

358
00:19:47,940 --> 00:19:48,980
than play with him.

359
00:19:51,540 --> 00:19:52,700
He was scary,

360
00:19:52,700 --> 00:19:53,580
talkative

361
00:19:53,700 --> 00:19:55,380
and self-righteous.

362
00:19:56,060 --> 00:19:57,380
His wife and friends

363
00:19:57,380 --> 00:19:59,020
dared not tell him to bathe more,

364
00:19:59,620 --> 00:20:00,740
so he didn’t know

365
00:20:00,740 --> 00:20:02,340
how bad he smelled.

366
00:20:03,900 --> 00:20:05,660
So I told myself

367
00:20:06,380 --> 00:20:07,820
that being wronged,

368
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:09,620
especially by those

369
00:20:09,620 --> 00:20:11,020
who couldn’t

370
00:20:11,020 --> 00:20:11,780
punish me

371
00:20:12,500 --> 00:20:13,540
was better than

372
00:20:13,740 --> 00:20:16,300
being laughed at secretly

373
00:20:16,580 --> 00:20:17,620
by people

374
00:20:18,260 --> 00:20:20,500
who either said nothing

375
00:20:20,580 --> 00:20:22,700
or cursed me behind my back.

376
00:20:23,580 --> 00:20:24,660
That way,

377
00:20:24,940 --> 00:20:26,460
when I saw Yu Jing

378
00:20:26,460 --> 00:20:27,540
criticizing me ruthlessly,

379
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:29,580
I actually found him less annoying

380
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:31,700
but pitiful

381
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:32,660
and a bit adorable.

382
00:20:33,380 --> 00:20:34,980
How could I still be mad at him?

383
00:20:38,740 --> 00:20:39,860
His Majesty

384
00:20:39,860 --> 00:20:41,020
scolded Princess Fukang in public.

385
00:20:41,900 --> 00:20:42,660
Then,

386
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:45,300
then Yaoyao was fine.

387
00:20:45,820 --> 00:20:47,220
The Empress jumped in

388
00:20:47,540 --> 00:20:48,500
and said how much

389
00:20:48,860 --> 00:20:50,860
the princess treasured that thing.

390
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:53,220
His Majesty must’ve felt bad

391
00:20:53,580 --> 00:20:54,700
for her.

392
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:56,220
So today...

393
00:20:58,500 --> 00:20:59,500
He promised

394
00:21:00,620 --> 00:21:01,980
that he’d come every night

395
00:21:03,020 --> 00:21:04,420
before the baby is born.

396
00:21:05,980 --> 00:21:06,860
I’ll wait for him.

397
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:18,060
If it was Su Shunqin...

398
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:19,820
Scholar Su?

399
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:22,540
Don’t you appreciate him?

400
00:21:22,860 --> 00:21:24,620
You even asked me to copy his works

401
00:21:25,220 --> 00:21:27,500
and said he was young but talented.

402
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:29,180
He always had fresh angles

403
00:21:30,380 --> 00:21:32,180
and he believed that poems and essays

404
00:21:32,420 --> 00:21:34,420
should express facts and true feelings.

405
00:21:35,460 --> 00:21:37,740
We should learn from Bai Juyi,

406
00:21:38,180 --> 00:21:39,180
a great poet in Tang Dynasty.

407
00:21:39,820 --> 00:21:40,940
Don’t pile up empty rhetoric

408
00:21:41,140 --> 00:21:43,020
or confuse others intentionally.

409
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:47,220
Your education has been paid off

410
00:21:47,460 --> 00:21:49,260
and you did learn things from me.

411
00:21:50,260 --> 00:21:50,980
You’re right.

412
00:21:51,700 --> 00:21:53,980
Aside from Su Shunqin’s unparalleled talent

413
00:21:53,980 --> 00:21:55,020
and vast knowledge,

414
00:21:55,460 --> 00:21:56,500
what’s even rarer

415
00:21:56,700 --> 00:21:58,220
is his pure heart.

416
00:21:58,740 --> 00:22:00,980
Articles are to tell facts.
Poems are to express feelings.

417
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:02,740
Good poems and articles

418
00:22:02,860 --> 00:22:04,420
should include ambition,

419
00:22:04,620 --> 00:22:06,660
kindness and warmth.

420
00:22:07,180 --> 00:22:08,820
Feelings should originate from the inside,

421
00:22:09,380 --> 00:22:11,540
and then sprout and grow, and bloom eventually.

422
00:22:12,020 --> 00:22:13,580
That’s how a masterpiece is produced.

423
00:22:15,100 --> 00:22:18,180
You like him so much.

424
00:22:18,460 --> 00:22:19,780
When he

425
00:22:19,780 --> 00:22:21,380
condemned you harshly,

426
00:22:21,900 --> 00:22:23,740
wouldn’t you feel hurt?

427
00:22:25,980 --> 00:22:27,940
Su Shunqin is from a prestigious family

428
00:22:27,940 --> 00:22:29,100
and became famous when he was young.

429
00:22:29,620 --> 00:22:30,700
Naturally, he’s confident,

430
00:22:30,700 --> 00:22:31,660
scholarly

431
00:22:32,300 --> 00:22:34,100
and can be really mean sometimes.

432
00:22:35,060 --> 00:22:36,780
He could drive me so mad and embarrassed

433
00:22:36,980 --> 00:22:37,940
that I’d rather

434
00:22:38,260 --> 00:22:39,580
bang my head on the pillar.

435
00:22:40,340 --> 00:22:41,700
Don’t be mad.

436
00:22:44,140 --> 00:22:45,100
I’m not.

437
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:48,100
So when he

438
00:22:48,540 --> 00:22:49,900
infuriated me,

439
00:22:49,900 --> 00:22:51,060
I’d say to myself

440
00:22:52,420 --> 00:22:54,940
that however famous he is,

441
00:22:55,220 --> 00:22:56,660
he’d still have to bow to me

442
00:22:56,700 --> 00:22:58,020
according to the rules

443
00:22:58,900 --> 00:23:00,700
and follow my every order.

444
00:23:01,620 --> 00:23:02,540
I could promote

445
00:23:02,540 --> 00:23:03,620
or demote him anytime.

446
00:23:05,620 --> 00:23:08,300
I’ve been given tremendous power

447
00:23:08,820 --> 00:23:10,420
right after I was born.

448
00:23:11,500 --> 00:23:12,780
Loyal officials feared

449
00:23:12,860 --> 00:23:14,140
that I’d abuse it

450
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:15,300
and indulge myself.

451
00:23:15,380 --> 00:23:16,700
Doing too much is better than doing little.

452
00:23:17,140 --> 00:23:17,860
So,

453
00:23:18,900 --> 00:23:20,300
even if he was wrong about me,

454
00:23:21,140 --> 00:23:22,300
I’d let him continue.

455
00:23:23,540 --> 00:23:25,060
He stood there speaking while I sat comfortably.

456
00:23:25,740 --> 00:23:26,660
He’d get tired

457
00:23:26,860 --> 00:23:28,740
and take his leave eventually.

458
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:32,780
Father,

459
00:23:33,300 --> 00:23:34,780
if Madam Zhang comes at me again,

460
00:23:35,500 --> 00:23:37,380
I’ll take a deep breath.

461
00:23:37,980 --> 00:23:39,580
If that doesn’t work,

462
00:23:39,940 --> 00:23:41,100
I’ll tell myself

463
00:23:41,740 --> 00:23:42,660
that she’s

464
00:23:42,660 --> 00:23:44,220
a fatherless,

465
00:23:44,340 --> 00:23:45,700
uneducated crazy woman.

466
00:23:46,100 --> 00:23:47,580
I’ll only say it in my head.

467
00:23:47,980 --> 00:23:49,260
No one will hear it.

468
00:23:53,180 --> 00:23:53,940
Alright.

469
00:23:55,300 --> 00:23:56,300
Well,

470
00:23:56,660 --> 00:23:58,540
you don’t need to tell me either.

471
00:24:02,940 --> 00:24:03,700
So,

472
00:24:04,300 --> 00:24:05,820
are we good now?

473
00:24:22,820 --> 00:24:24,940
I’ll restring them.

474
00:24:25,820 --> 00:24:26,780
Mother said

475
00:24:27,500 --> 00:24:28,620
broken jade pieces

476
00:24:28,700 --> 00:24:30,420
can be put together by gold.

477
00:24:31,420 --> 00:24:32,620
You gave it to me.

478
00:24:33,700 --> 00:24:34,660
However mad I am,

479
00:24:34,660 --> 00:24:35,740
I won’t throw it away.

480
00:24:36,380 --> 00:24:37,460
Even if

481
00:24:37,700 --> 00:24:39,340
you throw my gifts away,

482
00:24:39,340 --> 00:24:40,780
I’ll get them back.

483
00:24:43,420 --> 00:24:44,180
Father,

484
00:24:44,940 --> 00:24:46,940
I’ll be a good girl

485
00:24:47,980 --> 00:24:49,180
and won’t upset you again.

486
00:24:50,620 --> 00:24:52,180
You’re always the best.

487
00:24:54,740 --> 00:24:55,460
Father,

488
00:24:55,940 --> 00:24:57,300
where are the desserts?

489
00:25:03,300 --> 00:25:04,340
There’s nothing left,

490
00:25:04,340 --> 00:25:05,620
but I already

491
00:25:06,060 --> 00:25:08,060
told the kitchen to make more for you.

492
00:25:08,180 --> 00:25:09,420
You can have them tomorrow

493
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:10,300
at breakfast.

494
00:25:13,620 --> 00:25:14,340
Father,

495
00:25:14,580 --> 00:25:15,340
I want you

496
00:25:15,340 --> 00:25:16,580
to promise me one more thing.

497
00:25:16,940 --> 00:25:17,540
What is it?

498
00:25:18,940 --> 00:25:19,780
Next time,

499
00:25:19,780 --> 00:25:21,180
when you bring me desserts

500
00:25:21,300 --> 00:25:22,580
to comfort me,

501
00:25:23,780 --> 00:25:26,100
if I ignore you or refuse to take them,

502
00:25:26,180 --> 00:25:27,500
don’t give up.

503
00:25:27,660 --> 00:25:28,780
Force me to take them.

504
00:25:35,260 --> 00:25:36,100
Fine.

505
00:26:02,860 --> 00:26:04,420
You chatted with Huirou for so long

506
00:26:04,620 --> 00:26:06,580
that your throat must be sore.

507
00:26:07,540 --> 00:26:08,380
Have some tea.

508
00:26:15,620 --> 00:26:17,300
Zuixinglai is still coughing.

509
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:19,020
I want to look after him tonight

510
00:26:19,580 --> 00:26:21,780
in case of him burning up again,

511
00:26:22,700 --> 00:26:24,020
so I won’t invite you to stay tonight.

512
00:26:26,980 --> 00:26:28,540
Once Zuixinglai recovers,

513
00:26:29,580 --> 00:26:30,500
you’re free

514
00:26:30,700 --> 00:26:31,660
to come and taste

515
00:26:31,780 --> 00:26:34,100
my honey ginkgo

516
00:26:34,340 --> 00:26:35,300
and scented tea.

517
00:26:45,860 --> 00:26:46,660
Alright.

518
00:27:43,300 --> 00:27:45,580
Over four months have passed

519
00:27:45,780 --> 00:27:47,300
since Your Majesty issued the decree

520
00:27:47,540 --> 00:27:50,180
to carry out the reform.

521
00:27:50,980 --> 00:27:53,900
As Deputy Chief Han said,

522
00:27:54,820 --> 00:27:57,020
laying off redundant officials

523
00:27:57,300 --> 00:27:59,340
= Zhang Dexiang, courtesy name Xiyan =
terrorizes the rest.

524
00:28:00,500 --> 00:28:02,940
Efficiency is rising.

525
00:28:03,540 --> 00:28:05,340
The backlog of work

526
00:28:05,740 --> 00:28:06,940
is shrinking.

527
00:28:07,700 --> 00:28:08,540
Problem is,

528
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:10,340
as far as I know,

529
00:28:10,900 --> 00:28:12,660
over 20% of officials

530
00:28:13,340 --> 00:28:17,140
are laid off in Hedong Province along.

531
00:28:17,900 --> 00:28:19,500
Members of the royal family

532
00:28:19,940 --> 00:28:21,420
and decedents of heroes

533
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:25,220
= Ouyang Xiu, courtesy name Yongshu =
who lost their honorary posts are many.

534
00:28:25,580 --> 00:28:29,700
Complaints have flooded in.

535
00:28:34,860 --> 00:28:37,980
I’m not against the reform

536
00:28:38,540 --> 00:28:39,940
but I think

537
00:28:40,340 --> 00:28:42,820
we should take it slow.

538
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:45,140
Give those people

539
00:28:45,140 --> 00:28:46,420
some time to prepare.

540
00:28:46,900 --> 00:28:47,700
Otherwise,

541
00:28:48,020 --> 00:28:49,220
a person’s career

542
00:28:49,500 --> 00:28:51,260
will be destroyed overnight,

543
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:53,780
and his whole family will be in despair.

544
00:28:54,540 --> 00:28:55,900
It’s against the longstanding tradition

545
00:28:55,940 --> 00:28:58,420
of giving civil officials better treatment

546
00:28:58,900 --> 00:29:01,900
and violates Your Majesty’s fundamental principle

547
00:29:02,020 --> 00:29:03,540
of benevolence.

548
00:29:04,860 --> 00:29:05,980
With all due respect.

549
00:29:15,020 --> 00:29:16,300
Please enlighten me, Prime Minister Zhang.

550
00:29:17,860 --> 00:29:18,860
Who

551
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:20,580
and what

552
00:29:21,100 --> 00:29:23,100
destroy that person’s career

553
00:29:23,340 --> 00:29:24,380
and family?

554
00:29:29,700 --> 00:29:33,300
Isn’t it obvious, Censor Ouyang?

555
00:29:33,540 --> 00:29:34,380
Yes.

556
00:29:35,100 --> 00:29:36,940
I also don’t understand

557
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:39,700
how come Prime Minister Zhang

558
00:29:39,700 --> 00:29:41,940
twisted facts that are so clear.

559
00:29:44,100 --> 00:29:46,340
What did I twist?

560
00:29:49,140 --> 00:29:50,260
What destroyed

561
00:29:50,260 --> 00:29:52,500
those people’s careers

562
00:29:52,860 --> 00:29:56,060
are their laziness, irresponsibility

563
00:29:56,500 --> 00:29:58,580
and selfishness.

564
00:29:59,140 --> 00:30:01,580
Your Majesty’s decree

565
00:30:01,580 --> 00:30:03,700
is issued

566
00:30:03,700 --> 00:30:04,860
to remove such laziness, irresponsibility

567
00:30:04,860 --> 00:30:06,780
and selfishness

568
00:30:06,780 --> 00:30:08,060
completely

569
00:30:08,100 --> 00:30:10,260
from our court.

570
00:30:11,540 --> 00:30:12,900
How could you claim

571
00:30:13,380 --> 00:30:15,460
it was the dismissal

572
00:30:15,620 --> 00:30:17,260
that destroyed their career?

573
00:30:20,860 --> 00:30:21,580
Your Majesty,

574
00:30:23,020 --> 00:30:23,980
in my opinion,

575
00:30:24,900 --> 00:30:26,700
laziness, irresponsibility

576
00:30:26,940 --> 00:30:28,780
and selfishness

577
00:30:29,380 --> 00:30:32,540
slow down the court, burden the state

578
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:33,580
and waste money.

579
00:30:34,020 --> 00:30:34,980
What’s worse,

580
00:30:35,660 --> 00:30:37,660
court officials learn from each other,

581
00:30:37,940 --> 00:30:39,540
local administrations imitate the Capital,

582
00:30:39,700 --> 00:30:42,020
and the low-ranking copy the high-ranking,

583
00:30:42,020 --> 00:30:44,340
resulting in an epidemic.

584
00:30:45,220 --> 00:30:47,620
If no actions are taken soon,

585
00:30:48,220 --> 00:30:50,180
once the court is corrupted

586
00:30:50,260 --> 00:30:51,780
from the inside out,

587
00:30:51,940 --> 00:30:53,580
and the whole state is infected,

588
00:30:54,140 --> 00:30:58,380
the corrupted will win, the mediocre will obey

589
00:30:59,020 --> 00:31:00,100
and the loyal

590
00:31:00,180 --> 00:31:02,980
will become their common enemies

591
00:31:02,980 --> 00:31:05,060
and can’t survive.

592
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:06,380
So,

593
00:31:07,700 --> 00:31:09,700
how could we

594
00:31:09,700 --> 00:31:11,700
take it slow

595
00:31:13,340 --> 00:31:15,740
or give them time to prepare?

596
00:31:16,660 --> 00:31:19,020
When they were slack in their work

597
00:31:19,020 --> 00:31:20,420
and wasted government fund,

598
00:31:20,420 --> 00:31:22,620
they should’ve been prepared

599
00:31:22,900 --> 00:31:24,060
for this day to come.

600
00:31:39,860 --> 00:31:41,340
Back to a month ago,

601
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:44,220
= Fan Zhongyan, courtesy name Xiwen =
when I reviewed local officials

602
00:31:44,220 --> 00:31:45,940
in the judicial system,

603
00:31:46,500 --> 00:31:48,180
Scholar Fu

604
00:31:48,220 --> 00:31:50,620
also felt sad for the dismissed officials.

605
00:31:51,900 --> 00:31:53,060
He said

606
00:31:53,980 --> 00:31:55,340
a name was crossed off,

607
00:31:55,700 --> 00:31:57,140
then a whole family would weep.

608
00:31:57,820 --> 00:31:59,100
Hearing that,

609
00:31:59,300 --> 00:32:00,540
I asked him

610
00:32:00,700 --> 00:32:01,940
to show me

611
00:32:02,500 --> 00:32:03,700
the list of officials

612
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:06,020
I dismissed that day.

613
00:32:17,980 --> 00:32:18,860
Inside

614
00:32:20,020 --> 00:32:21,300
are the names

615
00:32:22,020 --> 00:32:23,900
I crossed off that day.

616
00:32:35,220 --> 00:32:36,740
I invited Scholar Fu

617
00:32:37,180 --> 00:32:38,660
to review with me

618
00:32:38,660 --> 00:32:39,620
their salaries,

619
00:32:40,140 --> 00:32:42,140
whether they took bribes from subordinates

620
00:32:42,260 --> 00:32:44,300
or merchants under their administration,

621
00:32:44,900 --> 00:32:47,300
and their properties and land.

622
00:32:48,380 --> 00:32:50,660
It’s been confirmed

623
00:32:50,940 --> 00:32:52,180
that none of them

624
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:54,020
has done anything beneficial

625
00:32:54,620 --> 00:32:55,620
to the state

626
00:32:55,620 --> 00:32:57,620
or our people.

627
00:32:57,940 --> 00:32:59,220
Among them, even the poorest

628
00:32:59,820 --> 00:33:01,980
bought more houses

629
00:33:02,540 --> 00:33:03,580
with their savings

630
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:05,740
than ten well-off families combined.

631
00:33:07,020 --> 00:33:08,180
None of them

632
00:33:08,380 --> 00:33:08,900
went broke

633
00:33:09,660 --> 00:33:10,420
after being dismissed

634
00:33:10,660 --> 00:33:12,140
from their posts.

635
00:33:12,580 --> 00:33:13,620
Apparently,

636
00:33:14,140 --> 00:33:16,260
it’s not that the dismissal

637
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:18,540
is going too fast or sharp,

638
00:33:18,860 --> 00:33:20,780
but it’s too late.

639
00:33:21,980 --> 00:33:23,540
They’ve wasted

640
00:33:23,540 --> 00:33:25,220
too much money from the court

641
00:33:25,220 --> 00:33:26,380
and our people.

642
00:33:28,820 --> 00:33:31,700
So what if one name is crossed off,

643
00:33:32,700 --> 00:33:34,980
a family will weep?

644
00:33:36,340 --> 00:33:37,460
If it were not them,

645
00:33:37,460 --> 00:33:39,220
the locals

646
00:33:39,220 --> 00:33:40,340
would all end up weeping.

647
00:33:42,380 --> 00:33:43,180
Right now,

648
00:33:43,420 --> 00:33:44,580
spare the majority from tears

649
00:33:45,420 --> 00:33:47,060
is more important than that of a family.

650
00:33:48,300 --> 00:33:50,900
I have no regret.

651
00:34:15,820 --> 00:34:17,660
= Di Qing, courtesy name Hanchen =
Double-check the security in the city.

652
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:19,140
My squad

653
00:34:19,140 --> 00:34:20,620
is responsible

654
00:34:20,700 --> 00:34:22,300
for Envoy Pang’s safety.

655
00:34:23,620 --> 00:34:24,300
Yes.

656
00:34:27,380 --> 00:34:28,380
Once the negotiation begins,

657
00:34:28,700 --> 00:34:30,060
release all eagles

658
00:34:30,060 --> 00:34:30,820
from the cages.

659
00:34:31,060 --> 00:34:31,740
Yes.

660
00:35:06,740 --> 00:35:07,620
Rise.

661
00:35:14,020 --> 00:35:14,900
A few years ago,

662
00:35:15,820 --> 00:35:17,140
when you worked at the Court of Judicial Review

663
00:35:17,620 --> 00:35:19,020
and the Directorate of Education,

664
00:35:19,500 --> 00:35:20,340
I was surprised

665
00:35:20,340 --> 00:35:22,260
and impressed

666
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:23,220
by your graceful speeches.

667
00:35:23,980 --> 00:35:28,140
= Sima Guang, courtesy name Junshi =
Sadly, your parents passed away afterward

668
00:35:28,500 --> 00:35:29,740
and you went back home to mourn for their deaths.

669
00:35:31,300 --> 00:35:33,260
During that period,

670
00:35:33,260 --> 00:35:34,540
you didn’t stop writing.

671
00:35:35,220 --> 00:35:37,180
I’ve read your discourses

672
00:35:37,180 --> 00:35:38,140
on Ten Sages, The Four Rich

673
00:35:38,620 --> 00:35:39,700
and Mr. Jia.

674
00:35:41,460 --> 00:35:42,500
I’m benighted

675
00:35:43,020 --> 00:35:44,380
and don’t deserve

676
00:35:45,020 --> 00:35:46,100
Your Majesty’s compliment.

677
00:35:47,260 --> 00:35:48,460
My mourning period is over

678
00:35:48,860 --> 00:35:51,340
but I’ll miss my parents forever.

679
00:35:52,700 --> 00:35:54,100
Once I arrive in Fengcheng,

680
00:35:54,500 --> 00:35:56,900
I could only do my utmost to serve the country

681
00:35:57,340 --> 00:35:59,780
to repay Your Majesty’s trust.

682
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:06,140
What do you think

683
00:36:07,020 --> 00:36:08,180
about the dismissal?

684
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:15,900
It has to be done.

685
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:18,700
We should be familiar

686
00:36:18,700 --> 00:36:19,660
with the thoughts

687
00:36:20,060 --> 00:36:21,980
and complaints of the dismissed.

688
00:36:26,940 --> 00:36:29,340
The excess of officials damages the entire state

689
00:36:29,620 --> 00:36:30,540
and wastes resources.

690
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:31,420
It has to go.

691
00:36:32,260 --> 00:36:33,980
And resentment will rise.

692
00:36:35,140 --> 00:36:37,580
There are a large group of officials involved

693
00:36:37,700 --> 00:36:38,860
who’s connected

694
00:36:38,940 --> 00:36:40,340
with those still in-service.

695
00:36:41,220 --> 00:36:42,700
Promoting and demoting local officials

696
00:36:42,740 --> 00:36:44,900
also affect the administration there

697
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:47,460
including people,

698
00:36:47,460 --> 00:36:48,900
business and farming.

699
00:36:50,020 --> 00:36:51,620
So how deep their resentment is,

700
00:36:52,140 --> 00:36:53,540
how it will be vented,

701
00:36:54,340 --> 00:36:55,860
will it mislead people

702
00:36:55,860 --> 00:36:57,060
and incite revolt,

703
00:36:57,740 --> 00:36:59,580
will they collude with other officials,

704
00:37:00,020 --> 00:37:02,140
Your Majesty and ministers

705
00:37:02,260 --> 00:37:04,300
should get to the bottom of them.

706
00:37:06,860 --> 00:37:07,780
Excellent!

707
00:37:09,580 --> 00:37:10,780
You’re young

708
00:37:11,420 --> 00:37:12,900
and talented

709
00:37:13,220 --> 00:37:14,660
but more composed than others.

710
00:37:16,540 --> 00:37:18,460
I hope your time in Fengcheng won’t be in vain.

711
00:37:18,860 --> 00:37:19,780
If you have new articles,

712
00:37:20,340 --> 00:37:21,460
don’t forget to send them to me.

713
00:37:35,580 --> 00:37:37,780
It’s said that Lady Zhang

714
00:37:37,780 --> 00:37:39,500
should be given less favor.

715
00:37:40,100 --> 00:37:42,140
= Jia Changchao’s Wife =
In winter,

716
00:37:42,740 --> 00:37:45,060
cloth dyers

717
00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:47,300
= Wang Gongchen’s Wife, Xue Yuhu =
had to break the ice for water

718
00:37:47,500 --> 00:37:50,060
to complete His Majesty’s order.

719
00:37:51,860 --> 00:37:52,860
Ouyang Xiu

720
00:37:52,860 --> 00:37:55,100
strongly condemned this

721
00:37:55,340 --> 00:37:57,540
and claimed that His Majesty

722
00:37:57,540 --> 00:37:58,620
showed you too much favor

723
00:37:58,700 --> 00:38:00,220
to be tolerated

724
00:38:00,540 --> 00:38:02,140
and there will be punishment.

725
00:38:05,660 --> 00:38:06,820
In order to protect my child

726
00:38:06,980 --> 00:38:08,580
and spare His Majesty from his nagging,

727
00:38:08,580 --> 00:38:09,780
I asked for a demotion,

728
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:11,420
yet they’re still onto me.

729
00:38:14,060 --> 00:38:14,900
Ouyang Xiu

730
00:38:16,060 --> 00:38:17,660
is an evil vicious dirty rat.

731
00:38:17,900 --> 00:38:19,500
He’ll be punished.

732
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:22,620
If anything happens to my child,

733
00:38:23,340 --> 00:38:24,620
he’ll have to pay the price.

734
00:38:25,500 --> 00:38:27,060
I’ll let him pay!

735
00:38:27,940 --> 00:38:29,020
= Discourse on Lasting Cloudiness =

736
00:38:29,020 --> 00:38:29,780
Deputy Chief Fu,

737
00:38:30,020 --> 00:38:30,940
His Majesty is having lunch.

738
00:38:31,860 --> 00:38:32,780
Fu Bi?

739
00:38:33,740 --> 00:38:35,100
I’m waiting outside, Your Majesty.

740
00:38:35,700 --> 00:38:36,500
Come in.

741
00:38:45,420 --> 00:38:46,180
Your Majesty.

742
00:38:46,460 --> 00:38:47,260
Have a seat.

743
00:38:49,780 --> 00:38:51,100
Your Majesty, you are too busy

744
00:38:51,740 --> 00:38:53,260
to have lunch on time.

745
00:38:53,700 --> 00:38:55,180
Your health is more important.

746
00:38:59,140 --> 00:39:00,300
I skipped the meal

747
00:39:00,300 --> 00:39:01,340
cooked by the Imperial Kitchen on purpose

748
00:39:01,620 --> 00:39:03,980
in the name of being busy

749
00:39:04,500 --> 00:39:06,420
and asked others

750
00:39:06,620 --> 00:39:08,020
to buy buns from Ms. Wang’s shop

751
00:39:08,140 --> 00:39:10,660
and pork from Cao’s Deli near the Gate of Phoenix.

752
00:39:11,820 --> 00:39:13,100
Have you had lunch?

753
00:39:13,260 --> 00:39:13,940
Here.

754
00:39:14,100 --> 00:39:15,980
We can have buns

755
00:39:15,980 --> 00:39:16,820
and pork together.

756
00:39:16,860 --> 00:39:17,620
Thank you, Your Majesty.

757
00:39:17,860 --> 00:39:18,780
I’m waiting

758
00:39:19,100 --> 00:39:20,620
= Fu Bi, courtesy name Yanguo =
for Your Majesty’s decision

759
00:39:20,820 --> 00:39:22,460
so that I can go back to the Privy Council

760
00:39:22,460 --> 00:39:23,340
to send it to Yan’an.

761
00:39:25,100 --> 00:39:26,420
Is the peace talk between Pang Ji and Yuanhao

762
00:39:26,420 --> 00:39:27,300
