765
00:39:30,820 --> 00:39:31,700
and follow our calendar.

766
00:39:31,700 --> 00:39:33,300
He’ll return Kaolao, Liandao,

767
00:39:33,340 --> 00:39:34,620
Nan’an and Chengping to us.

768
00:39:35,060 --> 00:39:36,340
The boundary will be established

769
00:39:36,340 --> 00:39:37,300
and no one shall cross it.

770
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:38,580
The captives will all be returned as well.

771
00:39:39,580 --> 00:39:41,340
Pang Ji signed the treaty as requested.

772
00:39:41,940 --> 00:39:43,380
Regard Yuanhao as the Lord of Xixia.

773
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:46,620
Provide him with a seal, money and supplies,

774
00:39:46,940 --> 00:39:48,220
including 130,000 bolts of silk,

775
00:39:48,620 --> 00:39:51,380
50,000 taels of silver and 10,000 kilos of tea.

776
00:39:53,660 --> 00:39:55,180
Last month, he refused

777
00:39:55,540 --> 00:39:57,980
to abandon his title but why now?

778
00:39:59,980 --> 00:40:00,940
Isn’t it fishy?

779
00:40:02,220 --> 00:40:03,100
Last month,

780
00:40:03,700 --> 00:40:05,660
