were all civilians.

783
00:40:08,460 --> 00:40:09,340
After that,

784
00:40:09,340 --> 00:40:10,620
spies deployed

785
00:40:10,620 --> 00:40:11,700
by General Di Qing earlier

786
00:40:11,940 --> 00:40:13,140
spread the content of the negotiation

787
00:40:13,220 --> 00:40:14,500
among the public

788
00:40:14,940 --> 00:40:15,940
to let them know

789
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:17,900
that despise the casualties,

790
00:40:17,900 --> 00:40:19,180
Yuanhao was still unwilling

791
00:40:19,420 --> 00:40:20,580
to abandon his title,

792
00:40:21,540 --> 00:40:24,100
so the treaty couldn’t be signed,

793
00:40:24,620 --> 00:40:26,580
