794
00:40:26,940 --> 00:40:27,900
and we wouldn’t offer them

795
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:29,580
money, tea and silk.

796
00:40:30,060 --> 00:40:31,180
In the end,

797
00:40:31,700 --> 00:40:33,420
it resulted into a revolt.

798
00:40:33,420 --> 00:40:34,980
Officials were killed. Offices were burned.

799
00:40:35,620 --> 00:40:37,300
Even Yuanhao’s own guards joined the rebels.

800
00:40:37,820 --> 00:40:39,580
They marched straight to his palace

801
00:40:39,700 --> 00:40:40,820
and besieged his wives and children for days.

802
00:40:41,700 --> 00:40:43,180
If he didn’t sign the treaty,

803
00:40:43,620 --> 00:40:45,740
there would be a regime change.

804
00:40:46,980 --> 00:40:48,860
All our conditions

805
00:40:49,100 --> 00:40:49,980
have been met as expected.

806
00:40:50,300 --> 00:40:52,380
Given the current situation,

807
00:40:53,220 --> 00:40:54,900
if we drag it on for one more year

808
00:40:54,940 --> 00:40:55,860
and continue the lockdown and the ban on trade...

809
00:40:56,900 --> 00:40:58,620
Since we offered more money to Liao,

810
00:40:59,220 --> 00:41:00,660
Liao and Xixia have become mortal enemies.

811
00:41:01,620 --> 00:41:03,100
Frictions between their borders

812
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:04,060
