815
00:41:12,740 --> 00:41:13,820
Due to the markets at the border,

816
00:41:14,340 --> 00:41:15,660
trade tax there

817
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:18,100
already reached half a million before 1040 A.D.,

818
00:41:19,220 --> 00:41:20,780
way more than what we offered Xixia.

819
00:41:22,020 --> 00:41:23,220
And the military expense...

820
00:41:29,980 --> 00:41:31,020
Since they’ve reached

821
00:41:31,020 --> 00:41:31,980
an agreement,

822
00:41:32,500 --> 00:41:33,460
then it’s settled.

823
00:41:35,500 --> 00:41:36,380
Once this ends,

824
00:41:36,740 --> 00:41:38,740
soldiers and civilians in Shaanxi and Longzhong

825
00:41:39,620 --> 00:41:41,300
can finally enjoy a peaceful Spring Festival.

